      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "For the very bravest, there are really only a few unusual parts to setting up the Galaxy instance. The first is to use the QIIME 2 specific fork and branch described above, and the next is to ensure that you have the correct configuration for conda and a tool config file so that your generated tools are accessible. For hints on this, see our "
